short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Downloads all temu invoices for the current year across all temu domains.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of navigating through your Temu order history to find and download your invoices? Temu Invoice Downloader simplifies the process by allowing you to quickly download invoices for any of your past purchases.

Features:

One-click download of invoices directly from your Temu account.
Saves time by automatically fetching and organizing your invoices.
Perfect for keeping track of your business expenses or personal purchases.
Works seamlessly with your Temu order history.
How it works:

Install the extension.
Log into your Temu account.
Access your orders, choose the period and click "Start Download".
Stay organized and save time with Temu Invoice Downloader!
